Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.31,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You find out sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:56.67,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}この道に何も無くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.86,0:22:06.26,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}君が居る限り この場所から
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:10.28,oped-jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}唄うよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:02.36,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}alone……落在大地上的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:07.21,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}You cry 無法止住
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.22,0:21:11.87,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}現在 我們能聽見的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.99,0:21:16.80,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}是現實的不協調的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:21.44,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}在混雜著安堵和失落感的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.58,0:21:26.43,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}這個房間裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.53,0:21:31.28,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}我們是掌握未來的關鍵
