Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.31,0:21:49.31,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}you find out sunshine
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:56.67,oped-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}即使這條路上一無所有
